donations.donation_comment: Heard Trudeau didn’t like Americans donating...so I decided to donate again. FJT and FJB.

We love each and every one of you folks and the great sacrifice you're making for the Freedom of Canada!
PLEASE do not settle for anything less than Justin Trudeau's removal from office, otherwise everyone's effort will have been for not!  May our Lord Jesus Christ bless you and keep you safe!
You’re doing Canada proud! “God keep our land glorious and FREE”!
We are praying for success as well.

We pray for wisdom to be yours, for peace, and hope to flow to you all.  May the God and Father of our Lord Jesus, the creator of life, protect and supply your every need.  We are confident God has called each of you for this very task, at this very time, to win back freedom.  God always prevails. God speed.  Amen.
donations.donation_name: A fan of your great work.

donations.donation_comment: Way to go truckers! Hold the line! End all mandates for Canadians!
God bless you guys.  You are true heroes.  I am proud of us and wish you the best
Keep up the good fight, hold the line !!!!
God Bless you all! Let Freedom REIGN!
